&lt;h3 id="season-overview"&gt;Season Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This was the best season and season 1 was probably second best. The second season was just ok. Very interesting plot twist. I can't wait for the next season. The characters seem to have more death this season than last. I also found it interesting that they take a Biblical view that a trinity (although this one is a secular one) would make one Empire they way to rule. Very interesting angle coming from an the series book author who was a supposed atheist.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="best-episodes"&gt;Best Episodes&lt;/h3&gt;
